pageProduct.name: Swisse Kids Multi 60 Gummies
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Swisse Kids Multi Gummies are a premium quality, comprehensive formula containing important vitamins and minerals including vitamins C and D, zinc and iodine. Made with natural colours and flavours and no artificial sweeteners, these great-tasting gummies are 99.9% sugar free and are ideal for fussy eaters and growing children on the go.

Swisse Kids Multi Gummies are a premium quality, comprehensive formula containing important vitamins and minerals including vitamins C and D, zinc and iodine, to:
- Provide nutritional support for children to maintain general health and wellbeing and support healthy growth and development
- Help prevent dietary nutritional deficiencies
- Support nutrient levels in the body when dietary intake is inadequate

Benefits:
- Great tasting for fussy eaters
- Duo of natural flavours: mixed berry & tropical
- 99.9% Sugar Free
- No artificial sweeteners
- Naturally sweetened with Stevia
- No added dairy or lactose

Size: 60 Gummies

Warnings

Vitamin & mineral supplements should not replace a balanced diet. This medicine contains maltitol & mannitol (Total 2.8g per maximum daily dose) and may have a laxative effect or cause diarrheoa. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional

Ingredients

Biotin 7.5 mcg; Folic Acid 50 mcg; Nicotinamide 2.4 mg; Vitamin B1 (thiamine from thiamine nitrate) 185 mcg; Vitamin B2 (riboflavin) 210 mcg; Vitamin B5 (pantothenic acid from calcium pantothenate) 1.09 mg; Vitamin B6 (pyridoxine from pyridoxine hydrochloride) 210 mcg; Vitamin B12 (cyanocobalamin) 400 ng; Vitamin C (ascorbic acid) 35 mg; Vitamin D3 (colecalciferol) 5 mcg; Vitamin E (dI-alpha-tocopheryl acetate) 2.68 mg; Iodine (from potassium iodide) 75 mcg; Zinc (from zinc sulfate monohydrate) 2 mg.
Contains Sulfites.

No added lactose, yeast, egg, soy, artificial colours or flavours

Directions

2-8 years: Chew 1 gummy daily, during or immediately after a meal.
9-12 years: Chew 2 gummies daily, during or immediately after a meal.
Or as directed by a healthcare professional. Do not swallow whole.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
